 Fulp也对该剧大加赞赏，甚至提高了网站的上传限制，允许第八集上传到网站上。 ","date":"2006-04-22","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/e6/8b/464944_y62C9.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/e6/8b/464944_y62C9.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/e6/8b/464944_y62C9.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/e6/8b/464944_y62C9.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/e6/8b/464944_y62C9.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":0,"total":1,"score":5,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0}},"tags":[{"name":"WEB","count":3},{"name":"同人动画","count":2},{"name":"同人","count":1}],"eps":9,"collection":{"wish":1,"collect":4,"doing":0,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1}},{"id":4019,"type":2,"name":"四畳半神話大系","name_cn":"四叠半神话大系","summary":"身为大三学生的“我”，梦想着多采多姿的校园生活却过了两年毫无意义的生活。虽然入学时在众多社团中选择了网球社，但是因为无法与人对话而失去容身之处。这时，他遇上有同样际遇的小津，两人组成了在社团内外四处妨碍人恋爱、恶名昭彰的“黑色丘比特”。没有遇到小津的话肯定能与黑发少女过着缤纷的人生！如果那时候选了其他社团……","date":"2010-04-22","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/7f/c6/4019_f34f4.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/7f/c6/4019_f34f4.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/7f/c6/4019_f34f4.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/7f/c6/4019_f34f4.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/7f/c6/4019_f34f4.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":33,"total":15038,"score":8.6,"count":{"1":19,"2":10,"3":11,"4":36,"5":103,"6":332,"7":1365,"8":4264,"9":6078,"10":2820}},"tags":[{"name":"汤浅政明","count":4756},{"name":"MADHouse","count":2975},{"name":"森见登美彦","count":2140},{"name":"TV","count":1826},{"name":"小说改","count":1596},{"name":"平行宇宙","count":1521},{"name":"另类空想","count":1457},{"name":"2010年4月","count":1261},{"name":"轮回","count":1095},{"name":"2010","count":1028},{"name":"神作","count":783}],"eps":11,"collection":{"wish":7891,"collect":20853,"doing":1646,"on_hold":1188,"dropped":303}},{"id":41736,"type":2,"name":"装甲騎兵ボトムズ 孤影再び","name_cn":"装甲骑兵 孤影再临","summary":"OVA作品『装甲騎兵ボトムズ 赫奕たる異端』の後日談。『日経キャラクターズ!』誌2006年1月号に掲載後、大幅に加筆・修正の上『日経エンタ