属于众人的明日。 ","date":"2022-04-22","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/06/c5/361697_hGmKQ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/06/c5/361697_hGmKQ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/06/c5/361697_hGmKQ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/06/c5/361697_hGmKQ.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/06/c5/361697_hGmKQ.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":7315,"total":263,"score":5.9,"count":{"1":2,"2":2,"3":9,"4":20,"5":49,"6":105,"7":52,"8":14,"9":0,"10":10}},"tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":90},{"name":"蜡笔小新","count":72},{"name":"2022","count":53},{"name":"搞笑","count":31},{"name":"原创","count":23},{"name":"SHIN-EI","count":21},{"name":"シンエイ動画","count":9},{"name":"日本","count":9},{"name":"小林由美子","count":9},{"name":"漫画改","count":8},{"name":"ならはしみき","count":6}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":83,"collect":488,"doing":14,"on_hold":13,"dropped":16}},{"id":380229,"type":2,"name":"The Bad Guys","name_cn":"坏蛋联盟","summary":"　　故事的主角是五个无恶不作的坏蛋——风度翩翩的扒手“大坏狼”、见多识广的保险箱窃贼“贪心蛇”、冷静沉稳的伪装大师“美肚鲨”、暴躁易怒的打手“食人鱼”、伶牙俐齿的黑客专家“骇客蛛”闪亮登场，他们是最臭名昭著的“坏蛋联盟”。他们平时威风八面，四处作案，令人闻风丧胆。直到某一天，他们突然想成为模范公民，然而转型路途甚是艰难，且意外层出不穷，令人啼笑皆非。","date":"2022-04-22","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/cb/19/380229_3dhHd.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/cb/19/380229_3dhHd.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/cb/19/380229_3dhHd.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/cb/19/380229_3dhHd.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/cb/19/380229_3dhHd.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":3460,"total":497,"score":6.8,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":2,"4":8,"5":39,"6":128,"7":216,"8":82,"9":8,"10":13}},"tags":[{"name":"梦工厂","count":128},{"name":"剧场版","count":110},{"name":"欧美","count":106},{"name":"动画电影","count":86},{"name":"2022","count":75},{"name":"搞笑","count":65},{"name":"动物","count":60},{"name":"美国","count":39},{"name":"福瑞","count":30},{"name":"3D","count":29},{"name":"电影","count":25}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":89,"collect":832,"d